videos.title: Boros Goblins Got New Toys!
videos.description:
Goblins got a Headliner, Frontline Rush, and a new Siege to try. If this plan doesn't work? We can always rely on throwing all the goblins into Agatha's Soul Cauldron and cooking them for our other Goblins.

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkigndom.com/mtggoldfish
